name: Satpurush Hotel

reviews.review_text:
I have dined here twice as once was not enough. I had fish thali on the day I arrived and before leaving I made sure to relish the food again. Food is good, hygienic place and varieties available.
Make sure you know your allergies before you place your order.

After recommendation from the hotel staff and online reviews I went to this family run restaurant for a lunch. Ordered a goan fish thali and a plate of King fish which they offer as an add-on to the thali and not individually.
After placing the order you have to wait for 15-20 minutes as food is prepared fresh. Food was good and flavour full. Light on stomach but filling. I even asked for extra curry and was provided free of cost.
Only complaint is regarding the thickness of the fish but still manageable. Price is nominal as compared to what restaurants are charging in Goa.

They were playing old hindi movie songs from 70s which were very soothing. The setup is very basic and nothing fancy but clean and maintained. Plastic tables and chairs. This place is really popular and gets filled up in no time and sometimes even run out of fish so its better to call before going.

Parking is a challenge and they don't allow drinking alcohol or smoking inside their premises.

A place to try authentic Goan fish thali. The veg thali is also good. They have Kokam soda as well as some other cold drinks.
Service is okay. Half the things on the menu were not available in November.

description:
### Experience the Culinary Charm of Satpurush Hotel

Nestled in the vibrant locale of Pernem, Satpurush Hotel boasts an impressive rating of 4.3 stars from 658 reviews, reflecting its reputation as a culinary gem in the region. The restaurant has become a beloved destination for locals and visitors alike, particularly celebrated for its **thali** offerings (113 mentions), authentic **Goan food** (66 mentions), and delightful **fish curry** (18 mentions). With frequent praise for its home-like environment, Satpurush Hotel serves not just meals but warm experiences.

### Ambiance & Design

Step into Satpurush Hotel, and you’ll find a no-frills, yet welcoming atmosphere. The basic setup features plastic tables and chairs, invoking a humble charm rather than high-end flamboyance. Customers appreciate the cleanliness and maintenance of this family-run restaurant, where the soothing strains of **old Hindi movie songs from the ’70s** add a nostalgic touch to the dining experience. The decor may be unpretentious, but it stands out for its comfort and warmth, mirroring the heartiness of the meals served.

![Satpurush Hotel Ambiance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdkrCjdIqgcT7_JJlOe7rCjJKq0IeDz2uyLvtc345MP7ugI9V6hQDFWfxgB8TJIIPxRuFd2yB4w2PWYgOn562d81eCCkb34PonxPVvSZuBSbU9kfqgYoNjkARxtaAgRFWCEk7DRS=w750-h563-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

At the heart of Satpurush Hotel's offerings is the famed **Goan fish thali**, which has turned many first-time visitors into repeat diners. Reviewers commend the **flavorful preparation** that retains a light feeling while being thoroughly satisfying. The fish dishes, such as the **King fish**, are prepared fresh and can take a little time to arrive—15 to 20 minutes—ensuring each plate is bursting with flavor.

The presentation of the food is inviting, with sections thoughtfully arranged on the thali, making for an appealing visual feast. The culinary experience also extends to vegetarian options, including a praised **veg thali**. Noteworthy mentions of **Kokam soda** and other refreshing drinks round out the experience and highlight the commitment to providing authentic local flavors.

![Goan Fish Thali](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdlZD9bEIzm2yMY0KRRXhujhTBkJxYuixVmwvRMfG5fjkII1rSYACqMhUgT9xXSdSUKtihzexKHUwOLcD3sBROHPVjywItXvig2yUg1NlMB7t1kHK6aImzmcit6vYIhGSFIVOcQ=w375-h281-p)

### Customer Experience & Service

The staff at Satpurush Hotel have been described as friendly and accommodating, enhancing the overall dining experience. Diners have commented on the generous service—such as providing extra curry at no charge—demonstrating their dedication to guest satisfaction. However, some reviews noted occasional limitations on the menu, with items being unavailable, so it may be wise to check beforehand.

For those planning a visit, the restaurant's popularity means it fills up quickly, and parking can be a challenge. It's advisable to call ahead, especially during peak times, to secure your place and avoid disappointment. Notably, the restaurant upholds a strict no-alcohol and no-smoking policy within its premises, ensuring a family-friendly atmosphere.

### Popularity & Reviews

The buzz surrounding Satpurush Hotel is palpable, with a significant number of patrons highlighting their experiences on social media and review platforms. Diner sentiment is overwhelmingly positive, reinforcing the establishment’s reputation as a must-visit for authentic Goan cuisine. Its accessibility in terms of pricing compared to other establishments in Goa adds to its appeal, as does the unfiltered authenticity of its culinary offerings.

![Vegetarian Options](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmw5TBxgOUWUuCdREHQwTG7UG0jKWaiSdjt1517P8yRH9tG5HOWvhQ-AuIkpmSNDs2Xh39i-MEnqEpgqU9OpeffUltB2UhXSVMARRYrsFMa8rglxEcVoKuQI8c3rjRQfBP_haJZVA=w375-h281-p)

### Visual Highlights

The experiences shared by customers are further enhanced by inviting visuals. From the vibrant array of the **fish thali** to the cozy setup of the restaurant, photos vividly depict the essence of Satpurush Hotel. These images serve as both a testament to the restaurant's culinary artistry and a portrayal of the welcoming environment in which these meals are enjoyed.

![Restaurant Entrance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdlXJlUTmcEcoItKzHuw6FjJCB5I643SdBLOux3cnFtomxPSYUpwQKRq0gWylmVzVJ-skE_ZmF8t0Bly56sGYYMQ10WE1k-zz1Jnr6aQpC9lKRMojYbrUgqSYKplqkTh5y24Vocb=w375-h281-p)

In conclusion, Satpurush Hotel is more than just a restaurant; it’s a heartfelt tribute to the flavors of Goa, served in a cozy setting where every dish tells a story. Whether you are a local or a traveler exploring the region, a visit here promises not just a meal, but a delightful dive into Goan culinary traditions.
